posts.name: Pradeep Kumar P
posts.cooked: should we just convert the given 20 attendees to vcard format as per schema or the prompt should also populate any missing data for those entries?

posts.name: Abhimanyu
posts.cooked:
Just convert them into vcard format. Don’t populate any missing data, leave them blank, i.e. "" empty string. You don’t have to get keys with empty values because the validator removes empty values anyway.
For ex:

{
      "fn": "Ashley Walker",
      "bday": "1980-08-05",
      "email": "",
      "tel": "",
      "adr": {
        "country-name": "Australia"
      },
      "org": "",
      "title": "Designer",
      "photo": "",
      "url": "",
      "nickname": "Ash"
    }

and

{
      "fn": "Ashley Walker",
      "bday": "1980-08-05",
      "adr": {
        "country-name": "Australia"
      },
      "title": "Designer",
      "nickname": "Ash"
    }

both work fine.
